item.description:
Anyone up for a change in indoor scenery?
Lets climb out to Central Rock Gym in Worcester for top roping and potentially some lead climbing.
Afterwards (around 9) we'll head out to Ralphs Diner for live music and post-climbing eats
http://www.ralphsrock...

Note if you havent climbed at CRG before you'll have to take a belay test to toprope
Note2 if you show up later than 6:45ish just look for me on the walls, I'll pair you up with someone
item.how_to_find_us: I'll be in the bouldering area near the entrance
item.name: Friday rocks in Worcester
